ai_summary.en: The crypto market is currently gripped by 'Fear,' as reflected by a BTC Fear & Greed Index of 29. Ethereum whales exhibit a cautious, near-neutral stance (-0.08), showing significant rebalancing without strong directional bets. In contrast, Solana's more speculative segment reveals a deeper bearish sentiment (-0.17) despite some stablecoin inflows, indicating less conviction. This divergence suggests a continued cautious short-term outlook, with SOL potentially facing more pronounced headwinds than ETH.
ai_summary.zh: 加密市场目前笼罩在“恐惧”情绪中，比特币恐惧与贪婪指数为29。以太坊巨鲸表现出谨慎的近中性立场（-0.08），交易量大但稳定币净流量为零，表明更多是资产再平衡而非强烈方向性押注。相比之下，Solana的投机性巨鲸情绪更为看跌（-0.17），尽管存在一些稳定币流入，整体信心不足。短期内，这种分歧预示市场将持续谨慎，Solana等投机性资产可能面临比以太坊更显著的下行压力。
